06:45.180 --> 06:49.160
What if already the design is the code?

06:49.160 --> 06:51.800
You can do a ton of stuff with Flex, CSS.

06:51.800 --> 06:54.500
It's actually quite advanced.

06:54.500 --> 07:01.920
So what if we say, let's do a developer-first design layout system?

07:01.920 --> 07:07.920
And we came up with Flex layout, and please do applaud here, because it's the first ever

07:07.920 --> 07:12.800
tool to have this, and it's open source.

07:12.800 --> 07:24.200
And the great thing about this is that this is not a gift from engineers to designers

07:24.200 --> 07:26.760
