07:29.880 --> 07:32.600
But actually, designers wanted this.

07:32.600 --> 07:34.440
So no compromises here.

07:34.440 --> 07:37.040
Everyone wins.

07:37.040 --> 07:42.160
We got 50 to 60 volunteers for the beta testing of this.

07:42.160 --> 07:47.440
